I cannot describe how overwhelmed I am to see all the love and support from everyone and I feel short of words to describe my beautiful journey to Miss Universe India. From being a small town girl who was denied too many opportunities to making my way to being called the first Miss Universe Jharkhand makes me believe that everything is possible when you have the passion in you to follow your heart. This journey reflects my hard work and determination. 

I am super lucky to have such supportive family who encourages me to follow my dreams and makes me believe that I can achieve whatever I desire. 🥹

Thank you @iamnikhilanand for believing in me and giving me this opportunity to represent my beautiful state Jharkhand. I will make sure to use my reign in the best way possible. Thanks @missuniverseindiaorg @glamanandsupermodelindia because of you I’ve had the opportunity to meet such incredible people all over the country and got to learn so much from everyone. This time I couldn’t win, but that does not mark the end of my journey. I believe this is just the beginning of a new chapter in my life, something even better is waiting for me. 🤞
Please keep supporting and loving. ♥️
Forever Grateful.🧿🙏
